Package: kalmanr
Type: Package
Title: R Bindings for the Kalman Filter Library
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Kalman", "Contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: R bindings for the header-only C++ Kalman filter library
    (https://github.com/pbosetti/kalman). Exposes a callback-driven Unscented
    Kalman Filter: supply the state-transition function f(x) and the measurement
    function h(x) as ordinary R functions operating on numeric vectors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: C++20
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
Imports: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Config/testthat/edition: 3
